reviewText: Not a collection of his better known songs, but good none the less. Fernando's very relaxed in this film, shot it apprears in a church. Not a professional filming but still good. I enjoyed it.

Both my wife and I love Ortega's music. He plays unique melodies, has a great voice for his songs, and has an endearing sense of humor. This album also has some great bonus features, such as song clips from a live concert.
